   "source": [
    "# GCC 智库研究抓取系统 v2.3\n",
    "**成都创新金融研究院** | 在 Google Colab 上运行\n",
    "\n",
    "---\n",
    "### 使用流程\n",
    "1. **Step 1** — 挂载 Google Drive（项目文件夹需已上传至 Drive）\n",
    "2. **Step 2** — 安装依赖\n",
    "3. **Step 3** — 配置 API Key（DeepSeek 或 Anthropic）\n",
    "4. **Step 4** — 运行抓取\n",
    "5. **Step 5** — 查看输出结果\n",
    "\n",
    "> **注意**：首次运行需完整执行所有 Step；之后每次只需运行 Step 4。"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## Step 1 — 挂载 Google Drive"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "from google.colab import drive\n",
    "drive.mount('/content/drive')\n",
    "\n",
    "# ⚠️ 修改为你的实际路径（Drive 内项目文件夹位置）\n",
    "PROJECT_DIR = '/content/drive/MyDrive/GccScraper'\n",
    "\n",
    "import os\n",
    "os.chdir(PROJECT_DIR)\n",
    "print(f'✅ 工作目录已切换至：{os.getcwd()}')\n",
    "print('当前文件列表：')\n",
    "for f in sorted(os.listdir('.')):\n",
    "    print(f'  {f}')"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## Step 2 — 安装依赖\n",
    "\n",
    "> 首次运行需要约 2–3 分钟。之后 Colab 会话内已安装，无需重复执行。"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# 安装 Python 依赖\n",
    "!pip install -q -r requirements.txt\n",
    "\n",
    "# 安装 Chromium（Playwright JS 渲染，仅首次需要）\n",
    "!pip install -q playwright\n",
    "!playwright install chromium\n",
    "\n",
    "print('✅ 依赖安装完成')"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## Step 3 — 配置 API Key\n",
    "\n",
    "使用 Colab Secrets（推荐）或直接填入环境变量。\n",
    "\n",
    "**推荐方式**：点击左侧 🔑 图标 → 添加 Secret，名称填 `DEEPSEEK_API_KEY`，值填你的 Key。"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "import os\n",
    "\n",
    "# ── 方式一：从 Colab Secrets 读取（推荐，Key 不出现在代码中）──────\n",
    "try:\n",
    "    from google.colab import userdata\n",
    "    os.environ['DEEPSEEK_API_KEY'] = userdata.get('DEEPSEEK_API_KEY')\n",
    "    print('✅ DeepSeek API Key 已从 Colab Secrets 加载')\n",
    "except Exception:\n",
    "    print('⚠️  未找到 Colab Secrets，请使用方式二手动填入')\n",
    "\n",
    "# ── 方式二：直接填入（测试用，勿提交到 Git）────────────────────────\n",
    "# os.environ['DEEPSEEK_API_KEY'] = 'sk-xxxxx'\n",
    "\n",
    "# ── 可选：切换为 Anthropic Claude ────────────────────────────────\n",
    "# os.environ['AI_PROVIDER'] = 'anthropic'\n",
    "# os.environ['ANTHROPIC_API_KEY'] = 'sk-ant-xxxxx'\n",
    "\n",
    "# 验证\n",
    "key = os.environ.get('DEEPSEEK_API_KEY', '')\n",
    "print(f'Key 状态：{\"已设置 (\" + key[:8] + \"...)\" if key else \"未设置 ❌\"}')"
   ]
  },
  {
